lCPU
=======

ABOUT
	lCPU was written to:
		1. Give specific load on CPU
		2. Show a simple example of working with POSIX threads

INSTALLATION
	git clone https://github.com/heckton/lcpu.git
	make

USAGE
	Use N threads and M bytes of memory during T seconds:
		./lcpu N T M
	M are optional argument:
		./lcpu N T

